{"tid":2456172,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大 愈怕聽歌","createTime":"2021-03-21T16:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T17:15:10.000Z","uid":253170,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e664603472614e25a020e7cd1fd124835ded89f","tid":2456172,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"每一首歌都記載著唔同既回憶<br />\n可能果個人已經無關痛癢<br />\n可能已經冰釋前嫌<br />\n可能連佢個樣都忘記左<br />\n<br />\n但每一首歌總會令自己回憶返當初既感覺<br />\n有當初既愉快 有回不去既童年<br />\n有曾經天跌下來既感受<br />\n<br />\n每次聽到曾經熟悉既歌<br />\n就好似重回果陣既感覺<br />\n<br />\n有既是無奈 是唏噓 是沉默"},{"pid":"238a6ccffb9d6a2841d5e7c9edb2a2061444abb0","tid":2456172,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主，做人都係直接打大佬好"},{"pid":"e475720838cd9b08c4c99ef1ff1100807a70fe8e","tid":2456172,"uid":252789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"證明你未夠大"},{"pid":"d56d5fdc4eb0f3c0a45a776f5be99e1ef3f406ce","tid":2456172,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"你聽嚟聽去得幾首<br />\n點同你玩"},{"pid":"3fe3c0b1382bf57cfb4fff26f32bb6c8be283190","tid":2456172,"uid":201768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"岩 出街帶耳機都淨係開消噪 唔想聽歌"},{"pid":"38305e912095523cbefa0b5c7907c33ce9e2b6ba","tid":2456172,"uid":127409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"應該係<br />\n<br />\n人愈大 愈怕聽舊歌"}]}